! $Id: whois_idle,v 1.1 2001/12/08 21:44:10 toast Exp $
Usage: FORMAT WHOIS_IDLE <format description>
  Controls how the whois line displaying a user's idle time appears.

  Valid format characters:
       N          Nick of whois target
       S          Number of seconds the whois target has been idle
       M          The equivalent of $tdiff(%S)

  This format has no effect if OLD_WHOIS_FORMAT is ON.

See Also:
